snippet.title: The Great War: Western Front - Announcement Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description: The Great War: Western Front is an intricate historical strategy game that was revealed during the Future Games Show at Gamescom 2022. The Great War: Western Front is coming to PC in 2023.
